#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:248
msgid "Performance Tips"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:250
msgid ""
"**Start with defaults**: The default parameters work well for most models"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:251
msgid "**Use TaylorSeer**: It typically improves both speed and quality"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:252
msgid ""
"**Tune R threshold**: Lower values = better quality, higher values = faster"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:253
msgid ""
"**SCM for extra speed**: Use `medium` preset for good speed/quality balance"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:254
msgid "**Warmup matters**: Higher warmup = more stable caching decisions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:256
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:258
msgid ""
"**SGLang-native pipelines**: Distributed support (TP/SP) is not yet "
"validated; Cache-DiT will be automatically disabled when `world_size > 1`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:260
msgid ""
"**SCM minimum steps**: SCM requires >= 8 inference steps to be effective"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:261
msgid ""
"**Model support**: Only models registered in Cache-DiT's "
"BlockAdapterRegister are supported"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:263
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:265
msgid "SCM disabled for low step count"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/performance/cache/cache_dit.md:267
msgid ""
"For models with < 8 inference steps (e.g., DMD distilled models), SCM will "
"be automatically disabled. DBCache acceleration still works."
msgstr ""

